     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA03d095n2-ptr" id="PJA03d095n2">2</a>
      
   <p>The one necessity, that is, gunpowder.</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA03d095n3-ptr" id="PJA03d095n3">3</a>
      
